XYDZ8av7VdF92D41vvVtY?filename=KCNtDFd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCNtDFd.png&h=df34bb36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一日跑翻班房個陣唔小心踢到張檯發現佢檯腳鬆鬆地<br />\n<br />\n於是踢左幾下之後變成咁再裝翻正佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYxwDWkTcmUWjgDsMSMxZdy3xKVZjkpoqxafXqFV4ehuY?filename=FhvbBse.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhvbBse.png&h=cd0d840d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住條撚樣有一次拍檯個陣直接拍到成張檯冧撚咗 笑到我地全班人仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿相認"}]}